00:09:02.839 --> 00:09:06.850
three clips for a total of three seconds out
of a ninety minute film. I think we have a

00:09:06.850 --> 00:09:11.540
pretty good case that this use isn't quantitatively
substantial. The other part of this is qualitative

00:09:11.540 --> 00:09:15.089
substantiality. This refers to a use that
borrows only the most valuable part of the

00:09:15.089 --> 00:09:19.029
source work. While I would argue that the
